<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.4">
<l>peṇpiṟantā reytum peruntuyarkāṇ kilēṉeṉ</l>
<l>ṟoṇcuṭarōṉ vārā toḷittāṉim maṇṇaḷanta</l>
<l>kaṇperiya cevvāyeṅ kārēṟu vārāṉā</l>
<l>leṇperiya cintainōy tīrppārā reṉṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying “I cannot see the great misery that reaches those born as women”</l>
<l>the [sun] with bright glow doesn’t come, lies hiden. Who measured this earth,</l> 
<l>my red-mouthed cloud bull with eyes that are big will not come.</l>
<l>Who will end the pain of [my] mind with thoughts that are big, o lord?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
